&lt;h1&gt;📞 Customer Service Representative (Residential Home Services)&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;📍 Kansas City, KS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;💲 $20–$24/hour&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🏡 Hybrid Opportunity Available After Training | Saturdays Required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Do You Thrive on Helping Others, Solving Problems, and Being Part of a Winning Team?&lt;/h2&gt;
