&lt;p&gt;At &lt;strong&gt;Garage Pros&lt;/strong&gt;, we&#39;re more than just a garage door company—we&#39;re a close-knit team committed to delivering exceptional service while building rewarding careers. As part of the Guild Garage Group family of brands, we&#39;re growing quickly and looking for an experienced Customer Service Representative who can make an immediate impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;ve worked in a fast-paced residential home services environment and love helping customers while keeping operations running smoothly, we&#39;d love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What You&#39;ll Be Doing&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll be the voice of Garage Pros, creating outstanding customer experiences while supporting our technicians and operations team. In this role, you will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Deliver exceptional customer service with professionalism, empathy, and urgency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Handle a high volume of inbound customer calls with confidence and efficiency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Schedule service appointments and coordinate technician routes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Communicate with customers via phone, email, and text regarding appointments and service updates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Work closely with technicians and office staff to ensure every customer receives outstanding service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maintain accurate customer records, notes, and documentation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Resolve customer concerns while providing timely and effective solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Identify opportunities to recommend additional services that benefit our customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Learn our services and become a trusted resource for customers and teammates alike.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What We&#39;re Looking For&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is not an entry-level customer service role. We are seeking an experienced professional who understands the pace and expectations of residential home services.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
